.TH NOXFORGE-DOCTOR 1 "July 2026" "NoxForge 3.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
noxforge-doctor \- inspect a NoxForge installation without changing it
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B noxforge-doctor
.RB [ \-\-json ]
.RB [ \-\-root
.IR path ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B noxforge-doctor
reports the installed package version, discovery and versions of NoxForge
components, safely readable active theme names, and a concise session summary.
It does not write files, apply a theme, clear caches, restart services, or
request privileges.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-json
Emit machine-readable JSON.
.TP
.BI \-\-root " path"
Inspect an absolute staged or system root instead of the running system.
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show command help.
.SH EXIT STATUS
Returns 0 for a complete, version-consistent installation, 1 for an absent,
partial, or mixed-version installation, and 2 for invalid command arguments.
.SH PRIVACY
The report omits usernames, hostnames, personal paths, and display contents.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /usr/share/noxforge/VERSION
Expected installed NoxForge version.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR rpm (8),
.BR dnf (8)
